                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090517-51-off295 t18090517-51-cd296"></join>, the furniture of a tent bed, value 4 s. a tablecloth, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090517-51-victim530" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Mayston
                        <interp inst="t18090517-51-victim530" type="surname" value="Mayston"></interp>
