                   - a pair of stockings, value 10 d. a pair of pattens, value 6 d. an apron, value 6 d. and two caps, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18090517-51-victim532" type="victimName">
                     Henry 
                     Smith
                  <interp inst="t18090517-51-victim532" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
